:<font size="15">עצם</font></div>

===Pronunciation===
עצם / ‛etsem / eh'-tsem

===Etymology===
From {{HH|6105}}; 

===Noun===
'''עצם'''

# A [[bone]] (as strong); by extension the body; figuratively the substance, that is, (as pronoun) selfsame: - body, bone, X life, (self-) same, strength, X very.

